title: I Love Vegetarian De Ra Sa
description: Vegan restaurant offering mostly Indonesian food with some Chinese dishes. Ample vegetable plates with choice of noodles or rice, plus a variety of mock meats. Located on the way to the airport on the Kuta Bypass Road. The nearest main intersection has an enormous white statue and the main hospital BIMC is located a little further up that main road.
streetAddress: Petrokoan Graha Tuban Kav 6, Jalan Bypass, Gusti Ngurah Rai 88 C, Kuta
